node.text: Weekend in Montecito 🌞 I got to share the new @penfolds California Collection with family & a few friends over the weekend. It was such a nice escape being able to share the quality time with some quality wine. We drank Bin 704, which is my favorite for its cherry & dark chocolate aroma. You can't go wrong with any of their 4 new Cabernets, it's been decades in the making. cheers xx #Penfolds #PenfoldsPartner #Ad

node.text: Golden Hour on the California coast. It’s a pleasure to team up with one of my favorite wine brands, @Penfolds to celebrate the launch of their new California Collection that’s been 20 years in the making. It was a perfect match, being able to explore the northern coast of my home state while treating myself to these beautiful new cabernets that were grown in the exact same region. cheers xx #PenfoldsPartner #Penfolds
